Fix v2 homepage logo: show full brand wordmark in header & footer

The live homepage (public/v2.html) cropped the logo into a 46x46 square
icon box sitting next to a hand-typeset "GO PREMIUM" wordmark, so the
real logo rendered tiny/squished and duplicated the text. Replace both
the header lockup and the footer typeset wordmark with the actual brand
logo image (logo.png navy-yellow in header, logo-white.png white-yellow
on the navy footer), sized to height with auto width. icon.png /
icon-white.png kept as onerror fallbacks.

